column10: This group contains concepts related to humanitarian relief when done by individuais. It is REQUIRED that the individual is from an organization, either as volunteer or as part of the job, which has a code or conduct compatible with Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement. This is the more generic type of what is considered _humanitarian_, but still an _strict_ type of humanitarian. This differentiation is likely to be more clear as more dictionaries for individuais are created.
